data.description: This West Oxnard, single-family residence is move-in ready and offers the perfect blend of comfort and style. With 4 bedrooms, 2 baths, and a spacious 1,480 sqft floor plan, this home provides ample space for your family. You'll have easy access to local amenities, schools, parks, and shopping centers. The neighborhood is known for its friendly community atmosphere and proximity to the vibrant culture and coastal attractions that make Oxnard a sought-after place to call home.This move-in ready gem is a rare find, offering not just a house, but a home where cherished memories await. Don't miss the opportunity to make this West Oxnard residence your own and start living the California dream!
